{"type":null,"faqId":9625,"title":"荣耀X1（7D-501u）7.0    怎样在 Windows 操作系统的计算机与荣耀 X1 7.0 间传输文件？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">您可以通过<b>设备文件管理（</b></span><b><span>MTP</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span><b><span>PC</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">助手（</span><span>HiSuite</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span><b><span>U </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">盘存储</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">三种连接模式在</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">与</span><span> Windows </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">操作系统计算机间同步文件。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">将荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">和计算机通过</span><span> USB </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">线相连时，如果计算机提醒您安装驱动程序，请根据提示安装。在荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">弹出的连接方式中选择一种连接模式并通过以下方式在二者间同步文件：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设备文件管理（</span><span>MTP</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">模式：勾选此模式后，您可以在计算机新出现的盘符中查看荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">内存和</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡上的文件，并与计算机间传输文件。您也可以通过</span><span> Windows Media Player </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">查看荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">内存和</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡上的媒体文件。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30104\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color:#339966;\"><span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>Windows XP </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">及以下版本的计算机需要安装</span><span> Windows Media<span>&nbsp; </span>Player 11 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">后才能使用</span><span>MTP </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">模式。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><b><span>PC</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">助手（</span><span>HiSuite</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">模式：勾选此模式后，计算机将会启动</span><span> HiSuite </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">程序。您可以通过</span><span> HiSuite </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">和计算机间传输文件或者在荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">上安装应用程序。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><b><span>U </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">盘存储</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">模式：勾选此模式后，您可以在计算机新出现的盘符中查看荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">中</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡上的文件，并与计算机间传输文件。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30105\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color:#339966;\"><span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">使用</span><b><span>U </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">盘存储</span></b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">模式连接计算机时，您将不能在荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">上读取到</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">上的内容。</span> \n</p>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;","faqTypeId":170,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":3,"unUseful":5,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"228","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Internet-Data-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396258885000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":1382,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}